RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select a.contract_ref_no, c.user_ref_no, syndication_ref_no, (select user_ref_no from OLTBS_CONTRACT where contract_ref_no = a.syndication_ref_no) as fac_user_ref_no, a.counterparty, d.short_name, a.currency, lBpks_services.fn_get_available_bal(a.contract_ref_no, greatest(e.today, a.value_date)) Principal_outstanding_bal, c.Auth_status from OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER a, OLTBS_CONTRACT_BALANCE b, OLTBS_CONTRACT c, OLTMS_CUSTOMER d, sttm_dates e where module = 'LB' and a.product_type = 'C' and a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no /*and nvl(b.Principal_Outstanding_bal,0) <> 0*/ and lBpks_services.fn_get_available_bal(a.contract_ref_no, greatest(e.today, a.value_date)) <> 0 and a.Version_No = c.Latest_Version_No and c.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and c.contract_status in ('A', 'Y') /*and c.contract_status = 'A' */ and c.branch = global.current_branch /* 29-JUN-2011 Flexcube V.CL Release 7.9, ITR1#44 changes start here */ and e.branch_code = c.branch /* 29-JUN-2011 Flexcube V.CL Release 7.9, ITR1#44 changes end here */ and d.customer_no = c.counterparty and d.RECORD_STAT = 'O' /*01-JUN-2011 Flexcube V.CL Release 7.9, CITIUS Retro, TILL#7740, changes start*/ /*06-MAY-2011 EURCITIPLC-LS#Special changes start*/ /*and c.department_code = :GLOBAL.sm_current_department*/ /*and ((c.department_code = :GLOBAL.sm_current_department and global.x9$ = 'CITIUS') or global.x9$ IN ('EURCITIPLC', 'PLNCITI', 'OFCL'))*/ /*06-MAY-2011 EURCITIPLC-LS#Special changes end*/ /*01-JUN-2011 Flexcube V.CL Release 7.9, CITIUS Retro, TILL#7740, changes end*/ /*24-JUL2015 EURCITIPLC#19945 changes start*/ AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR f, OLVW_USER_PRODUCTS g WHERE g.user_id = f.user_id AND g.product_code = f.product_code AND c.product_code = f.product_code AND c.branch = f.branch_code AND g.user_id = global.user_id)/*24-JUL2015 EURCITIPLC#19945 changes end*/ and (select count(*) from oltb_contract_event_log h where h.contract_ref_no = a.contract_ref_no and h.auth_status = 'A') > 0

SELECT a.PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description FROM LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD a, OLTMS_PRODUCT b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d WHERE a.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code AND a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND b.product_code = c.product AND c.participant_product IS NOT NULL AND a.product_code = d.product_code AND d.branch_code = global.current_branch AND d.user_id = global.user_id AND a.version_no = (SELECT MAX(version_no) FROM LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD WHERE contract_Ref_no = ?) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM oltms_product k, olvw_user_products s WHERE s.user_id = global.user_id AND s.product_code = k.product_code AND s.product_code = b.product_code) UNION(SELECT a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_BORR_DDPROD a, OLTMS_PRODUCT b, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD c, OLVW_AVL_PROD_BR_USR d WHERE a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code AND a.contract_ref_no = ? AND b.product_code = d.product_code AND d.branch_code = global.current_branch AND d.user_id = global.user_id AND a.version_no = (SELECT latest_version_no FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT WHERE contract_ref_no = ? AND a.customer_no = ? AND b.product_code = c.product AND c.participant_product IS NOT NULL) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM oltms_product k, olvw_user_products s WHERE s.user_id = global.user_id AND s.product_code = k.product_code AND s.product_code = b.product_code))

select a.ccy, b.ccy_name from LBTBS_BORROWER_CCY a, cytms_ccy_defn b, oltbs_contract c,olvws_product_currencies opc where a.ccy = b.ccy_code and opc.ccy_code = b.ccy_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO =? and opc.product_code = ? and a.contract_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no and a.version_no = c.Latest_version_no and nvl(a.block_ccy,'N')<>'Y' and b.record_stat = 'O' and b.auth_stat = 'A'
SELECT industry_code FROM oltm_industry WHERE auth_stat ='A' AND record_stat='O'

select a.lc_issuer,a.participant,b.CUSTOMER_NAME1 from lbtbs_contract_lcissuer_detail a, OLTMS_CUSTOMER b where a.contract_ref_no=? and a.lc_issuer is not null and a.event_seq_no = (select max(event_seq_no) from lbtbs_contract_lcissuer_detail where contract_ref_no=a.contract_ref_no) and b.CUSTOMER_NO = a.participant AND b.RECORD_STAT = 'O'
Select Admin_ID, Admin_name from OLTM_ADMINISTRATOR where Auth_stat = 'A'
select ccy_code, ccy_name from cytms_ccy_defn where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'
select branch_code, branch_name from oltms_branch where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'

select ac_gl_no, ac_gl_ccy, ac_gl_desc from oltbs_account a where (branch_code is not null or ac_or_gl = 'G') and gl_aclass_type <> '5' and ac_gl_rec_status = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A' and NVL(branch_code, ?) = ? AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE A.AC_GL_NO = X.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?) order by decode(nvl(ac_gl_ccy, '*'), ?, 1, 2), decode(nvl(cust_no, '*'), ?, 1, 2), ac_gl_no, branch_code

select a.status, b.description from oltms_product_status_master a , oltms_contract_statuses b where a.product = ? and a.status = b.status_code and b.status_type in ('C','B') and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' order by a.status_sequence
select DISTINCT RATE_TYPE, CCY_RATE_TYPE_DESC from cytms_rates, CYTMS_RATE_TYPE where cytms_rates.branch_code = global.current_branch AND cytms_rates.RATE_TYPE = CYTMS_RATE_TYPE.CCY_RATE_TYPE

SELECT COMPONENT FROM (SELECT COMPONENT FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_DFLT_SCHEDULES A WHERE PRODUCT = ? UNION Select COMPONENT From lftms_product_fee Where product_code = ? And nvl(stop_association, 'N') = 'N') WHERE COMPONENT NOT IN (SELECT COMPONENT FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE MAS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND COMPONENT_STATUS = 'V' AND EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LFTBS_CONTRACT_FEE DET WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND MAS.COMPONENT=DET.COMPONENT))

select a.contract_ref_no linked_to_ref, a.branch linked_to_branch, b.facility_name from oltbs_contract a, oltbs_contract_master b where a.product_type IN ('L', 'D', 'B', 'P', 'C') and a.contract_status in ('A', 'Y') and a.auth_status = 'A' and a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no and a.module_code = 'LB' and a.branch = global.current_branch and a.latest_version_no = b.version_no and b.value_date <= ? and nvl(b.maturity_date, '31-dec-75') >= nvl(?, '31-dec-75') and A.COUNTERPARTY = ? order by a.contract_ref_no

select a.PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD a,oltms_product b, oltms_product_master_ld c where a.PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and a.version_no = (SELECT max(version_no) from LBTBS_BORROWER_DRAWDOWN_PROD where contract_Ref_no = ?) UNION select a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE, b.product_description from lbtbs_contract_borr_ddprod a, oltms_product b, oltms_product_master_ld c where a.DD_PRODUCT_CODE = b.product_code and a.contract_ref_no = ? and a.version_no = (select latest_version_no from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no = ?) and a.customer_no = ? and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL and b.product_code = c.product and c.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT is not NULL
SELECT LOV, LOV_DESC FROM OLTM_USER_FIELDS_LOV WHERE FUNCTION_ID ='LBDDDONL' AND FIELD_NAME ='RATEBASIS'

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT * FROM ((SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, l.Line_Code || l.Line_Serial Linkage_Ref_No, 'F' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = l.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, l.Brn Branch, l.Line_Currency Currency, l.Description, l.Line_Expiry_Date Expiry_Date, l.facility_type facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Facility l, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE l.Record_Stat = 'O' AND l.Liab_Id = Cust.Liab_Id AND l.Once_Auth = 'Y' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND l.Availability_Flag = 'Y' AND Nvl('CCY', ?) = 'CCY' AND Nvl('LIABCIF', ?) = 'LIABCIF' AND Nvl('CNPTY', ?) = 'CNPTY' AND Nvl('PRDCD', ?) = 'PRDCD' AND Nvl('BRN', ?) = 'BRN' AND Nvl('CCY', ?) = 'CCY') UNION (SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, Pp.Pool_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'P' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = Pp.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, Pp.Branch_Code Branch, Pool_Ccy Currency, Pp.Pool_Description, NULL Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Pool Pp, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Pp.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Liab_Id = Pp.Liab_Id AND Pp.Once_Auth = 'Y' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A') UNION (SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, c.Collateral_Code Linkage_Ref_No, 'T' Linkage_Type, (SELECT Liab_No FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab WHERE Id = c.Liab_Id) Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Branch_Code Branch, c.Collateral_Currency Currency, c.Collateral_Description, c.End_Date Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Collat c, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Cust.Liab_Id = c.Liab_Id AND c.Available = 'Y' AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y') UNION (SELECT 'A' Default_Liab, c.Liab_No Linkage_Ref_No, 'L' Linkage_Type, c.Liab_No, Cust.Customer_No Customer_No, c.Liab_Branch Branch, c.Liab_Ccy Currency, c.Liab_Name, NULL AS Expiry_Date, NULL facility_type FROM Sttm_Core_El_Liab c, Sttm_Core_El_Liab_Cust Cust WHERE Cust.Liab_Id = c.Id AND c.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Record_Stat = 'O' AND Cust.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND c.Once_Auth = 'Y')) WHERE Customer_No = Nvl(?, ?) AND Linkage_Type = ? AND (('A' = ?) OR ('S' = ? AND Liab_No = ?) OR Default_Liab = ?)
SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO,A.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER A WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY A.CUSTOMER_NO

SELECT A.CUSTOMER_NO, b.short_name, b.gfcid FROM LbTBS_CONTRACT_BORROWERS A, oltms_customer b, olTBS_CONTRACT c where A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? and a.customer_no = b.customer_no and b.auth_stat = 'A' and b.record_stat = 'O' and a.contract_ref_no = c.contract_ref_no and a.Version_no = c.Latest_version_no and nvl(a.blocked,'N') = 'N' and c.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('Y','A') and exists (select 1 from olvws_product_customers o where o.product_code = ? and o.customer_no = b.customer_no) order by a.customer_no

SELECT x.CUSTOMER_NO,b.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM lbtbs_Contract_Borrowers x,OLTMS_CUSTOMER b where contract_ref_no = ? AND x.CUSTOMER_NO = b.CUSTOMER_NO AND b.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND version_no = (SELECT max(version_no) FROM lbtbs_syndication_master WHERE contract_ref_no = ?)
